commitResults.messageBody:
Fixes done in this Pull Request:

1. Tweaked validity check for complete order as it led to software misbehaving as the order disappears from the User Interface, but in reality it still exists within the Order List.
2. Fixed JsonStorage for the Order, as it previously did not store the Product details properly, this resulted in the software misbehaving and not performing as advertised in the User Guide and the product in the order not matching the one in the menu
